                     <interp inst="t17830723-96-off441" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830723-96-off441" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17830723-96-cd442" type="crimeDate">24th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-96-off441 t17830723-96-cd442"></join> last, twenty-seven yards of muslin, value 10 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17830723-96-victim983" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Jeremy
                        <interp inst="t17830723-96-victim983" type="surname" value="Jeremy"></interp>
